messages.message:
Cypress update:
• upstream-integrations is fixed for at least another once, we need to figure out how to get a permanent outlook mailbox :upside_down_face: 
• downstream-integrations broke due to a backend bug (go Cypress!) and a fix is coming soon
• I think search-app is failing due to one of the data sources issue that's been reported - will follow up on this one later after those fixes are merged
• payment migrated user is still failing @Victor Zeng - do you want to look into this? I can also take a look
• review-manager-dashboard is failing after the changes you made to the reviewer selector @Udit, I'll try to fix this
• documents-grid, file-list, and results-table (and sometimes advanced-apps) are all failing due to some weird mounting behavior in the view app page, I have a PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67115) up to fix it
a lot fewer failures than yesterday phew :raised_hands:
Yeah much better!! Turns out most of them were just those few build bugs
